## Error States

### Form field error → `<FormField error={...}>`

Per-field inline errors are handled by `<FormField>` automatically (see Forms section).

### Page / API error banner → `<ErrorAlert>`

For errors not tied to a specific field — network failures, API errors, permission errors:

```tsx
import { ErrorAlert } from "@/app/_components/error-alert";

{error && <ErrorAlert>{error}</ErrorAlert>}
```

Has `role="alert"` built in. Place above the form or the affected section.

### Panel / section inline error

For errors inside a content panel (not a form):

```tsx
{error && (
  <p className="font-sans text-sm text-destructive" role="alert">{error}</p>
)}
```

