## Empty States

Centered icon + description. Used when a list or feed has no content:

```tsx
<div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-20 px-6">
  <BrandSunburst s={64} className="text-ink/15 mb-6" aria-hidden="true" />
  <p className="text-center max-w-[280px] font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">
    {t("empty_message")}
  </p>
</div>
```

Text-only variant (for compact spaces like sidebars):

```tsx
<p className="py-8 text-center font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">
  {t("empty_message")}
</p>
```

