## Quick Reference

| Need | Use |
|---|---|
| Async button loading | `<Spinner>` — `@/app/_components/spinner` |
| Skeleton content loading | `animate-pulse` div with `bg-muted rounded-card` |
| Form label + input + error | `<FormField>` — `@/app/_components/form-field` |
| Page/API error banner | `<ErrorAlert>` — `@/app/_components/error-alert` |
| Page or section heading | `<PageHeader>` — `@/app/_components/page-header` |
| Auth page layout | `<AuthPageShell>` — `@/app/(public)/auth/_components/auth-page-shell` |
| App page layout | Shell in (app) layout; pages render main content only; optional `useSidebarOverrides` for sidebar state |
| Post-auth redirect | `redirectAfterAuth(user, router)` — `@/app/_libs/utils/auth` |
| Motion variants | `fadeUp`, `fadeUpLeft`, `slideInLeft`, `springGentle` — `@/app/_libs/utils/motion` |
| Per-item action menu | `<DropdownMenu>` from `@/components/ui/dropdown-menu` |
| Filter bar | Active/inactive pill buttons with `rounded-badge` |
| Card list stagger | `cardVariants` with `custom={index}` |
